am over the age of eighteen and not a party to the within action; my
business address is: TROOP MEISINGER STEUBER & PASICH,
LLP, 10940 Wilshire Boulevard, 8th Floor, Los Angeles, California
90024-3902.

On May 17, 1996, I served the foregoing documents described as :

