<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>Michael Jordan and Patrick Ewing and other basketball players filed this suit against the National Basketball Association challenging the league's salary cap, draft, and restricted free agency system. If they win, team owners will not be able to lock out the players next season, which they have threatened to do if the two sides cannot agree on a new labor agreement.</P>
<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>
<PRE>
