<P>The motion to discontinue action and the reply affidavit in support of the motion to discontinue action from the case between pop singer Billy Joel and his former manager Francis Weber. Plaintiffs filed a motion to discontinue action to avoid trial, acknowledging that defendants do not have ample resources to cover a judgment.</P>
