<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>Richard Kuh, appointed by a New York judge to investigate possible abuses in the handling of the estate of tobacco heiress Doris Duke and the circumstances of her death, filed this supplement to his April 20, 1995 report.</P>
<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>
<PRE>
