     the Part of Bernard Lafferty, U.S. Trust and
     Katten Muchin & Zavis (SCPA Section 702(8)) . . . . .47

          (1)  Bank's Loan to Its Designating
               Fiduciary . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  47
          (2)  Double Dipping? . . . . . . . . . . . . .  50
          (3)  Bank's Reporting a Duke-Lafferty
               Death-bed Gift. . . . . . . . . . . . . .  51
